=64C2A164\" /></td>\r\n			<td><img alt=\"Peut être une image de 8 personnes, personnes debout, personnes assises et intérieur\" src=\"https://z-p3-scontent.fnsi2-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t39.30808-6/331526467_1696580234094901_8164398946753831704_n.jpg?_nc_cat=102&amp;cb=99be929b-59f725be&amp;ccb=1-7&amp;_nc_sid=5cd70e&amp;_nc_eui2=AeGrTdvigT7BMKD7iehAybL6SUYiWvxwOWNJRiJa_HA5Y8noe1jVbJ5TVt3qBeWNGrNZB5_WigRw6OhbggMI6vBx&amp;_nc_ohc=9dzma9r8iIIAX9V4pFD&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=z-p3-scontent.fnsi2-1.fna&amp;oh=00_AfAeIgU-erOogiBVRf2VoDkpvg5xShvcwvHLhKY-A4Snyw&amp;oe=64C3AC55\" /></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img alt=\"Peut être une image de 6 personnes, personnes assises, personnes debout et intérieur\" src=\"https://z-p3-scontent.fnsi2-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t39.30808-6/331085906_3228937047396595_7795305793231092741_n.jpg?_nc_cat=103&amp;cb=99be929b-59f725be&amp;ccb=1-7&amp;_nc_sid=5cd70e&amp;_nc_eui2=AeHybxCHJqxxB_gZz8Y1GQjkRs4a2b1HU0BGzhrZvUdTQLEnoFK7B6uF3ZhtGOIRQypsMHhTGEVZ9Wg8CYLReKEC&amp;_nc_ohc=otE5UAc9BWoAX-VvuJp&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=z-p3-scontent.fnsi2-1.fna&amp;oh=00_AfBPq-oZtOJIxzGUqlKshxnW4SyzOx2MfSx0UUNaOi81_A&amp;oe=64C3C8B2\" /></td>\r\n			<td><img alt=\"Peut être une image de 5 personnes et personnes assises\" src=\"https://z-p3-scontent.fnsi2-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t39.30808-6/331915990_2710617139074852_7056205137578667504_n.jpg?_nc_cat=107&amp;cb=99be929b-59f725be&amp;ccb=1-7&amp;_nc_sid=5cd70e&amp;_nc_eui2=AeFQEdra9S1pZsPm5sZqbtd2CYu5Un2ZsD8Ji7lSfZmwP6c57BUPUWgfWR5xxuo1P0l935UQUk06JJ0MXkzEHYkP&amp;_nc_ohc=4tABrSvVRPsAX9P4a1G&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=z-p3-scontent.fnsi2-1.fna&amp;oh=00_AfB-_1VDCTv2BB2BBXs_Dh8hfMNIoPgmrSvVhYNUEWLH6Q&amp;oe=64C3BD0C\" /></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>-------------------------------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><em>LE SECRETAIRE GENERAL</em></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>ANGUISSA ANGUISSA Tobie</strong></p>', '62173230724', '2023-07-24', '14:04:30', '2023-07-24 14:04:30', '1235700', 0, 'BILO\'O ALAIN DIDIE